## 🎯 Objectives Achieved

### ✅ Core Backend Infrastructure
- **FastAPI Setup**: Complete async endpoints with dependency injection
- **Database Layer**: SQLAlchemy 2.0 + PostGIS with spatial indexing
- **Background Tasks**: AI service integration with proper error handling
- **File Management**: 10MB limit with MIME type validation
- **Rate Limiting**: Redis-based sliding window (10 requests/hour per IP)
- **Security**: Input sanitization and comprehensive error handling

### ✅ AI Service Integration
- **YOLOv8n Integration**: Working inference endpoint with confidence scoring
- **Severity Classification**: High/Medium/Low based on confidence and detection count
- **Fallback Handling**: Graceful degradation when AI service unavailable
- **Performance**: Sub-10s inference times achieved

### ✅ Frontend Implementation
- **Next.js 14**: TypeScript with strict typing and modern UI
- **Spatial UI**: Leaflet.js with interactive map and markers
- **Image Upload**: Drag-and-drop with preview and validation
- **Location Selection**: GPS auto-detection with manual fallback
- **Real-time Updates**: Server-Sent Events for live incident tracking
- **AI Feedback**: Enhanced AIResultCard with bounding boxes and points display

### ✅ Integration & Validation
- **Docker Orchestration**: Multi-service setup with proper networking
- **API Integration**: End-to-end flow from frontend to backend to AI service
- **Spatial Data**: PostGIS geography storage with SRID 4326
- **Event Streaming**: Redis-backed SSE for real-time updates
- **Comprehensive Testing**: E2E validation covering all critical paths

